112
00:10:33,490 --> 00:10:35,170
but out of disdain.

113
00:10:35,210 --> 00:10:36,630
With her scheming and means,

114
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:38,000
she could have a better life

115
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,670
