144
00:12:08,460 --> 00:12:10,420
This is a very popular meat.

145
00:12:10,770 --> 00:12:12,520
We can't be the only ones eyeing them.

146
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,800
Just do your best.

147
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:16,120
Don't worry

148
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:17,680
